PUT	/api/storymaps/{storyMapId}	更新指定校园故事地图:
示例请求体：
{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "description": "Updated description."
} (可选字段,仅发送要改的字段)

需要返回的格式：
{
  "storyMapId": "uuid-string",
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "authorId": "uuid-string",
  "createdAt": "timestamp",
  "coverImageUrl": "http://...",
  "location": {
    "locationId": "uuid-string",
    "lat": ...,
    "lng": ...,
  },
}